<p>修改 : <%= @tag.TAGNAME %>相关信息（如果想要修改其父目录，则需要sql语句执行修改）</p>
<form action="/hejia_tag_manage/subdirectories_update" method="post">
  <table border=1>
    <input type="hidden" name="type" id="type" value="edit"/>
    <input type="hidden" name="tagid" id="tagid" value="<%= @tag.TAGID %>"/>
    <tr>
      <td>名称</td>
      <td><input type="text" name="tagname" id="tagname" value="<%= @tag.TAGNAME %>" size=10/></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>pinyin</td>
      <td><input type="text" name="tagpinyin" id="tagpinyin" value="<%= @tag.TAGURL %>" size=10/></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td align=center colspan=2><input type="submit" value="更新"/></td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</form>